profile.bio: Co-Founder of Princeton Tech Meetup. Currently at Kiswe Mobile, developing iPhone/iPad apps. Princeton Toastmasters Club President. Former Java Web Dev Mgr. Have worked for Intercall, Scholastic and others. UIUC & Stevens Tech Grad.
